  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed roof extension by virtue of its design and prominent siting in the public realm, would detract from the existing continuous parapet line to the front and the clear, unobstructed views from the side that is currently enjoyed in this terrace row to the severe detriment of the character and appearance of the street scene and surrounding Mercers Road/Tavistock Terrace Conservation Area. The proposal is therefore contrary to Policies to D1, D4, D11 and D25 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002 and Islington's Conservation Area Guidelines 2005."
